gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 128, Magic 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Magic, 128-111. Jayson Tatum recorded 30 points, six rebounds, and four assists for the Celtics, with Payton Prichard adding 21 points (6-7 3PM) and five assists in the victory. Jalen Suggs tallied 19 points and four rebounds for the Magic in the loss. The Celtics have won 13 straight games at home this season and improve to 19-5 in the regular season, while the Magic fall to 16-8.
